WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:08.834
Hey, good morning family. How are y'all doing today? Well, praise the Lord. We have another video for you.

00:00:08.835 --> 00:00:19.759
I was praying last night and seeking the Lord, and he's talking to me a lot about things that are coming, things for my future, for my kids, and for what he has for us.

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:25.735
But a lot of you—I've noticed some of the emails say, "Oh, Brother Brandon, none of that's going to happen when we're here.

00:00:25.736 --> 00:00:34.427
We're going to be taken in the rapture before. We won't see any of that stuff."And I have to say, you're delusional.

00:00:34.428 --> 00:00:42.058
None of the other prophets are prophesying that. None of the other ministers are ministering that.

00:00:42.059 --> 00:00:50.703
What makes you think that God's only going to tell you this stuff? I have no idea why I'm the only one the Lord tells.

00:00:50.704 --> 00:01:01.445
He said, "Brandon, because I'm going to tell you, I have a lot of people try to be my friend."And you go, "Okay, can I talk to them?

00:01:01.446 --> 00:01:06.999
Can I hang out with them?"And the Lord says, "No, I've called you to be separate unto me.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:21.803
You won't have friends in this because they will influence the way I talk to you because their opinions don't line up with what I'm saying."That's interesting because I will reach out and want to talk to people and the Lord said, "That's the last conversation.

00:01:21.804 --> 00:01:30.233
Don't continue to do that. Don't do that because their opinions don't line up with what I'm telling you, Brandon.

00:01:30.234 --> 00:01:37.657
I'm trying to lead you in a direction and warn my people what's coming."Now, what they're hearing, that's between them and God.

00:01:37.658 --> 00:01:42.048
I'm not here to judge that. I'm here to follow what the Holy Spirit tells me to tell you.

00:01:42.049 --> 00:01:47.051
And if it witnesses with you and it bears witness in your spirit, then go by it.

00:01:47.052 --> 00:01:50.742
If it doesn't, put it on the shelf. But at least I can say I told you so.

00:01:50.743 --> 00:02:12.381
The Lord told me, he said, "There's a difference, Brandon."He said so many people say, "Lord, all these people say you're humble."Even big ministries say, "Oh, you're humble."And he said, "Brandon, humility is something of the heart.

00:02:12.382 --> 00:02:21.407
Either you have it or you don't. Either you recognize that it's Christ in you or you don't.

00:02:21.408 --> 00:02:39.829
It's black and white."And I can tell you, ladies and gentlemen, if you really knew how my education was and who I really am as a person, I am—in the natural—what I perceive is a very insecure person a lot of times about things.

00:02:39.830 --> 00:02:43.867
But the Lord told me, he said, "Brandon, I've called you to be secure in me.

00:02:43.868 --> 00:03:03.290
It doesn't matter what men say about you."And he has me on a path to tell you all what he says, and I stand with him regardless of what everybody else says—how popular you can be or who invites you to their house or their conference or whatever.

00:03:03.291 --> 00:03:12.958
I don't care. I prefer really to stay right here in my garden praying and talking to the Father and looking at my flowers.

00:03:12.959 --> 00:03:17.411
I don't care about all that other stuff. This is just me. I'm real.

00:03:17.412 --> 00:03:22.557
All that other crap doesn't matter. People try to boost up an ego real quick.

00:03:22.558 --> 00:03:27.002
I see a lot of ego in the body of Christ in the upper leadership.

00:03:27.003 --> 00:03:32.430
A lot of people with big heads that feel they're like Saul. You know what it's like?

00:03:32.431 --> 00:03:42.390
It's like Saul whenever he lost the anointing; David had it and he thought he was still called of God and God was still speaking to him.

00:03:42.391 --> 00:03:50.115
They are as dry as a desert spiritually and they're still pretending that they've got it and they don't have it anymore.

00:03:50.116 --> 00:04:01.438
I've seen it a lot and they walk around with this big puffed-up ego and spiritual head thinking the Lord's still talking to them and they haven't had a fresh word in years.

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:13.661
They're still running off of twenty-year revelation. But God is a now God and he speaks fresh revelation all the time.

00:04:13.662 --> 00:04:22.154
I've tried to tell you all the people that you see in the forefront now won't be there soon.

00:04:22.154 --> 00:04:29.474
And you'll see a new generation of Davids rising up beyond anybody's comprehension of what's about to take place.

00:04:29.475 --> 00:04:37.599
But it's not to glorify man. It's to glorify God. And it's about him getting the glory.

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:43.615
Ego and resume, ego and platform is no more. It's all about Jesus.

00:04:43.616 --> 00:04:52.994
And I'm telling you, to get the work done that he wants done, you're going to see the glory move in services that you had no idea he'd move into.

00:04:52.995 --> 00:05:00.836
You think he'd be in some big shot's service, but you'll hear that the glory showed up in a nobody's service in the natural.

00:05:00.837 --> 00:05:07.160
Do you know what I'm saying? Just because Jesus could move through them because they didn't have a puffed-up head.

00:05:07.161 --> 00:05:11.526
Their head was deflated. It was just because they were hungry.

00:05:11.527 --> 00:05:21.092
For "blessed are those that hunger and thirst after righteousness, for they will be filled."So that's what I had to say.

00:05:21.093 --> 00:05:26.269
And then there's a lot of you who get mad about big preachers having a lot of money.

00:05:26.270 --> 00:05:30.119
And I heard you all say certain ministers, "Oh, they're the devil.

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:40.029
They have this, they have that."And as a person who cleaned for big ministries most of his life, yeah, it's frustrating.

00:05:40.030 --> 00:05:51.702
You see they have multi-million dollar homes, multi-million dollar furniture, flying around in multi-million dollar planes, private airplanes, private islands, going out and doing stuff.

00:05:51.703 --> 00:05:57.656
And the Lord blessed them. And you'd see a lot of the lay people in the body of Christ, they would do without.

00:05:57.657 --> 00:06:06.930
You see a lot of them working for nothing and they're sowing. They're sowing hard. They give hard.

00:06:06.931 --> 00:06:18.525
And I believe there is a balance of things that the Lord wants to get across with people because you've been burnt and you give up on things.

00:06:18.526 --> 00:06:25.017
Well, I don't believe God wants us blessed, and then you start talking bad about the man of God.

00:06:25.018 --> 00:06:31.812
I learned this: no matter how blessed I saw them, I would look at what they gave.

00:06:31.812 --> 00:06:39.056
I would look at how they gave. I would look at their lifestyle of how they would help other people.

00:06:39.057 --> 00:06:49.839
And the Bible says that if you give, it shall be given unto you—good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over will men give into your bosom.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:58.959
But if you are not in ministry and you don't have those huge platforms whenever people aren't giving those multi-million dollar checks to you, how do you make it?

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:07.230
Because my mom and dad, we were all grunts in the ministry. All of us were. And they struggled. I mean, I live on food stamps.

00:07:07.231 --> 00:07:17.820
And you go, "Man, we believe in God just to get through."And we're always looking for that Holy Ghost handshake—the gifts and surprises in the mail.

00:07:17.821 --> 00:07:23.116
A lot of times they never come. You would sow and sow and believe God.

00:07:23.117 --> 00:07:32.045
But I got a hold of the scripture that he gives you power to get wealth, that he anoints your hand to do something.

00:07:32.046 --> 00:07:56.998
And I got to the point where I started realizing—I'd watch how the world had ideas and the millionaires had ideas to get wealth through jobs and businesses and things like that, but they weren't janitors, but they set up side hustles.

00:07:56.999 --> 00:08:06.391
They would do real estate, they would do stocks or whatever. So I sow my seed and I start asking God for wisdom.

00:08:06.392 --> 00:08:19.262
Asking the Father, "Show me how to become the head and not the tail."And I'm telling you, working a Monday through Friday, 8 to 5 job, making minimum wage, you're never going to do it.

00:08:19.263 --> 00:08:23.465
You're going to have to believe God for a creative idea to get wealth.

00:08:23.466 --> 00:08:29.973
I would say in the natural it's to own your own business, to have a company, to create.

00:08:29.974 --> 00:08:38.855
Ask God for what you're good at. Do something that God has anointed you to do.

00:08:38.856 --> 00:08:42.002
I've said this before, ladies and gentlemen, but it's the truth.

00:08:42.003 --> 00:08:54.597
You never see people working at Lowe's or Home Depot 8 to 5, Monday through Friday, just believing they'll get into upper management and become wealthy.

00:08:54.598 --> 00:09:01.086
We just made a good living, but you struggled. You have your little house and your little car, and we're satisfied.

00:09:01.087 --> 00:09:07.966
We're happy. But the Lord wants you to have above and beyond all that you dare ask or think.

00:09:07.967 --> 00:09:12.754
God is a blessed God. And they said, 'Well, you're a prosperity preacher.'You're right.

00:09:12.755 --> 00:09:17.963
You're right, I am. I want to see the body of Christ not struggle because I was there.

00:09:17.964 --> 00:09:23.465
I remember. Then the Lord gave me ideas to start detailing cars.

00:09:23.466 --> 00:09:29.963
I started detailing cars because I worked for a mega-ministry, and they taught me how to detail cars.

00:09:29.964 --> 00:09:32.668
They taught me how to extract carpets. I cleaned airplanes.

00:09:32.669 --> 00:09:41.161
I did things for them; I learned how to do things, wax stuff, clean, and get stains out.

00:09:41.162 --> 00:09:46.840
I learned all that. So, I took the knowledge that I had from doing that, and I created a business.

00:09:46.841 --> 00:09:54.400
I started detailing cars on the side, and I'd clean five extra cars. I'd work my tail end off.

00:09:54.401 --> 00:10:05.492
On the weekends, I only took off on Sundays to go to church because I had to work that afternoon at the church to shut it down, and I'd go out and do all day Saturday.

00:10:05.493 --> 00:10:11.603
So, I worked sometimes seven days a week until I built up enough money and we put it back.

00:10:11.604 --> 00:10:15.960
We struggled, but it took time. I would sow, and I believed God.

00:10:15.961 --> 00:10:22.143
I would detail those cars and find people in the church and hand out flyers, whatever it took, saying, 'Hey, listen.

00:10:22.144 --> 00:10:27.214
I've got a detail business.'And they would say, 'Oh, yeah, Brandon, whatever.'I'd charge a hundred bucks.

00:10:27.215 --> 00:10:30.166
A hundred bucks! Man, I was so excited to get that hundred bucks.

00:10:30.167 --> 00:10:35.265
I took that $100 and I would sow my 10% and take a little extra and believe God.

00:10:35.266 --> 00:10:44.233
If I could get an extra four cars on a Saturday, I'd work all day long for $400. I thought that was amazing because I worked hard for it.

00:10:44.234 --> 00:10:49.436
After supplies and everything, it wasn't that much because I had to buy my supplies.

00:10:49.437 --> 00:10:57.376
It was a lot, but I just kept going, building it, and working year after year.

00:10:57.377 --> 00:11:20.380
I kept building my clientele up, and then the Lord said, 'I want you to do something else.'So, I got some dogs and started raising champion bloodline dogs for special needs kids—companion dogs for therapy.

00:11:20.381 --> 00:11:25.615
You know, when my daughter got diagnosed with autism, a therapy dog was really good for her.

00:11:25.616 --> 00:11:30.506
So, I started having ideas of how to help out therapy kids and making money doing that.

00:11:30.507 --> 00:11:36.799
What I'm trying to say is then Diana had the idea for eBay, and everybody knows we've done eBay and Poshmark, and that's what we do.

00:11:36.800 --> 00:11:48.719
So, instead of getting frustrated with people and seeing their blessing, look at the seed they sowed and then believe God for your idea.

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:54.377
Believe God. When you sow your seed, you start sowing into good ground.

00:11:54.378 --> 00:12:03.331
And that's whenever I started realizing that not all ground was created equal in the eyes of the Lord.

00:12:03.332 --> 00:12:05.946
People got mad at me when I started saying this kind of stuff.

00:12:05.947 --> 00:12:08.892
They get irritated because pastors don't like you to say that kind of stuff.

00:12:08.893 --> 00:12:15.359
They get frustrated because they don't want you to try to hamper their churches or whatever.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:22.047
I'm not trying to cause any ripples or waves; I just state what I feel and what the Lord shows me.

00:12:22.048 --> 00:12:29.168
So, over the course of time, the Lord has anointed me to do more and more.

00:12:29.169 --> 00:12:34.158
I want you to understand: God wants you blessed. God wants you prosperous.

00:12:34.159 --> 00:12:42.161
God wants you to have more than enough. I bring all this up because I know there's a lot of you that struggle.

00:12:42.162 --> 00:12:58.577
I try not to touch on finances very much because people get really annoyed when you talk about finances, especially in the body of Christ, because it seems that you all feel that it's been abused and I get a lot of hate from it.

00:12:58.578 --> 00:13:08.602
So I try to help you if you will listen, because I've been around the biggest of the biggest in the natural and I've watched it.

00:13:08.603 --> 00:13:18.529
I've watched how they sow. I've learned from some of the biggest names in ministry there are.

00:13:18.530 --> 00:13:25.586
The Lord has allowed me to see it. I've seen what they have, what they wear, and their closets.

00:13:25.587 --> 00:13:35.751
I've seen what the Lord's done with their lives. People criticize it, but I've seen what they give and how they sow.

00:13:35.752 --> 00:13:48.638
People go, 'Well, you know,'whatever, man. I'm going to be honest with you: I could care less what they have if their ground is good.

00:13:48.639 --> 00:13:57.462
If their ground is good and it produces and you sow into it—say they had a billion dollars and their ground is good.

00:13:57.463 --> 00:14:08.048
You don't know what it takes to make ground good. What makes 100-fold ground, and what sacrifice does it take to have 100-fold ground soil?

00:14:08.049 --> 00:14:14.958
Instead of criticizing them because they are blessed, look at their soil.

00:14:14.959 --> 00:14:20.525
Do they have good soil? Is their soil producing a 100-fold? Yes.

00:14:20.526 --> 00:14:28.419
Then there are not very many that do. So don't criticize it. Just sow into it and reap the fruit off of it.

00:14:28.420 --> 00:14:34.638
Don't be dumb, because what you talk against, you're not going to receive from.

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:45.234
You've got to not talk against them because if you do, you don't receive the harvest off of it. I've learned: don't criticize.

00:14:45.235 --> 00:14:51.759
You get annoyed sometimes and your flesh goes, 'Man, I wish that was mine,'because that's covetousness.

00:14:51.760 --> 00:15:04.232
But I just go, 'Hey, whatever you have for me, Father, bless me in my house.'Father, you're no respecter of persons, and what you did for them, you'll do for me.

00:15:04.233 --> 00:15:12.723
So I know, God, if I sow into good ground, you said that you reap back a 100-fold return—some 30, some 60, and 100-fold.

00:15:12.724 --> 00:15:20.799
So that's what I'm trying to tell you all: ask God for a creative idea and look at the grounds that are blessed.

00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:28.244
Find the blessed 100-fold ground and sow into it. And I'm telling you, God will bless your hands, too.

00:15:28.245 --> 00:15:35.874
But some people keep giving in the same place, same time, same everything, and they don't ever see.

00:15:35.875 --> 00:15:54.159
I look at this: if you go and visit a church and everybody in the congregation is broke, check yourself. There's a problem if everybody's broke.

00:15:54.160 --> 00:16:00.772
Now, you go into some mega-churches and there's a lot of seeker-friendly and their soil is not good or whatever.

00:16:00.773 --> 00:16:08.523
I'm not saying that just because you have a rich congregation means there's anointing there or the hand's favor is there.

00:16:08.524 --> 00:16:23.248
Sometimes I go into some seeker-friendly churches and you go, 'Well, it's just because you've got a lot of doctors and lawyers here that are just looking for something.'But I'm talking about, in general, you can feel when the spirit of God is on something.

00:16:23.249 --> 00:16:39.618
Am I making sense? I hope I am because I'm trying to teach y'all something here—what Diana and I watch for. Are the people blessed? Are they spiritually set free?

00:16:39.619 --> 00:16:49.012
Are they being fed the meat of the word so that they can stand on the word of God when the storms of life come?

00:16:49.013 --> 00:17:01.315
Or are they all busted, their marriage is defeated, they're divorced, they've got sickness, and their kids are run wayward and strung out on drugs, sleeping around, and doing bad things?

00:17:01.316 --> 00:17:13.788
Is the congregation successful spiritually just as much as they are in the natural? That's what I'm trying to say. I hope that makes sense.

00:17:13.789 --> 00:17:35.255
I get a lot of flack from the emails, and Diana tells me, 'I want you to address some things and tell them where we are with that.'And so in these videos, coming up with content and telling you all things, some may be a hit and a miss.

00:17:35.256 --> 00:17:39.672
I'm listening and just pressing into Him. It's a lot of responsibility.

00:17:39.673 --> 00:17:48.407
I pray y'all have mercy on me. I'm doing it. Lord, I just thank You for every single person that's representing.

00:17:48.408 --> 00:18:05.279
He said, "I want you to take communion with My people."I just had Chipotle chips and, Lord, we're going to take communion with Chipotle chips today.

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:11.500
To God be the glory. It's not religious. It's personal. And Jesus wants you to be personal with Him.

00:18:11.501 --> 00:18:15.449
Don't get all flaky. People get all hyperspiritual and you got to have the wafer.

00:18:15.450 --> 00:18:18.072
And that's what I've said before. He just looks at the heart.

00:18:18.073 --> 00:18:28.994
He looks at the inward man and He just says, "Man, My kid, he loves Me and he wants to have fellowship with Me today."We don't have to go "thee"and "thou."I just go, "Jesus, I'm here.

00:18:28.995 --> 00:18:40.600
I just want to have fellowship with You today. Let's sit down and talk."Do you understand? He's wanting to be your Father and a friend.

00:18:40.601 --> 00:18:49.752
He's not some God up there saying, "Where have you been?"Hey, He's there with His daddy arms and saying, "Hey, come on in, kids.

00:18:49.753 --> 00:18:59.669
Let's go have some coffee."Do you understand? God is a God of ever-present help in a time of need. And He wants to be your buddy. He wants to be your friend.

00:18:59.670 --> 00:19:08.432
He wants to see that you have everything your heart desires and that you are fulfilled in every area of your life.

00:19:08.433 --> 00:19:16.937
Above all things, that you prosper and be in health even as your soul prospers, full of joy.

00:19:16.938 --> 00:19:29.826
I hope that blesses you because I'm telling you that's what He wants, and a lot of you don't know Him. You know about Him, but you don't know Him.

00:19:29.827 --> 00:19:38.358
You know a lot about Him and He may know a lot about you, but does—and He knows you—but does He know you?

00:19:38.359 --> 00:19:44.370
I mean, is He allowed—do you allow Him to be in your life? Do you allow Him to be Lord over your life?

00:19:44.371 --> 00:19:52.362
Does that make sense? Do you allow Him to be Lord over your life? You still keep Him at arm's length.

00:19:52.363 --> 00:19:59.300
"I just have enough, just maybe I can just scratch into heaven. I just want to scratch my way into heaven.

00:19:59.301 --> 00:20:09.191
I just ride the fence."So stupid, whenever He wants to have a relationship with you and have abundance to the full until it overflows.

00:20:09.192 --> 00:20:20.171
There's a helicopter. So, Father, we just thank You for all our law enforcement as they fly by. That's medical.

00:20:20.172 --> 00:20:30.399
Father, whoever's on that medical helicopter, we thank You, Lord, that You protect that family.

00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:35.683
Lord, we thank You that You heal the bodies. Everybody that has something, God, there's so many needs.

00:20:35.684 --> 00:20:40.479
There's so many people that are broken. There's so many people that need more.

00:20:40.480 --> 00:20:45.279
There's so many people that are walking in lack in their bodies and health.

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:54.460
And You said Your words are life to those that find them and health to all their flesh. So, Father, we find Your word today.

00:20:54.461 --> 00:20:59.396
We find You and we thank You, Lord, that You said in Your word, by Your stripes, we're healed.

00:20:59.397 --> 00:21:05.026
Now, I agree—by Your stripes, they're healed. And I just pray for every person that's on here today.

00:21:05.027 --> 00:21:09.562
And we call healing and wholeness and wellness over them right now in Jesus'name.

00:21:09.563 --> 00:21:15.634
And we thank You, Lord, that You said that they're healed. And Father, we thank You, Lord, that this is the meal that heals.

00:21:15.635 --> 00:21:19.941
And we take this body in the name of Jesus. And we lift it up before You, God.

00:21:19.942 --> 00:21:30.558
And we thank You that You were wounded for our transgressions, You were bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon You, and with Your stripes, we are healed.

00:21:30.559 --> 00:21:54.399
And we thank You, Lord, for this body right now. Now, Lord, we thank You for the blood.

00:21:54.400 --> 00:22:10.239
Never be in a hurry, Father, to be with You. Always in a rush. People, just be patient and wait on You.

00:22:10.240 --> 00:22:18.879
It's like, what else we have to do in life other than to find You? All the other stuff doesn't matter.

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:24.059
Lord, we take the blood of Jesus and we apply the blood of Jesus over everything we do.

00:22:24.060 --> 00:22:29.219
We plead the blood of Jesus over our families and over our sins and over everything, Father.

00:22:29.220 --> 00:22:33.682
And You said if we make much of the blood, the blood makes much of us.

00:22:33.683 --> 00:22:38.832
And we apply the blood over our lives today. And we say thank You, Father, for the blood.

00:22:38.832 --> 00:22:44.103
And we plead the blood over us, Father. For where the blood is applied, Satan cannot touch it.

00:22:44.104 --> 00:22:50.639
And I thank You for the blood today, God. I cover my family in the blood of Jesus.

00:22:50.640 --> 00:23:08.316
Take the blood now. Lord, thank You that You're my healer. We're healed today. Well, God is good.

00:23:08.317 --> 00:23:16.879
And I pray these videos are doing something for your spiritual walk because I try to get real with y'all.

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:28.479
Because I get tired of super flaky Christian preachers. And they say, "You ain't saying what all these other preachers are saying,"because I'm not called to.

00:23:28.480 --> 00:23:38.074
I'm called to say the hard things. And the Lord told me, He said, "You're going to say some hard things and people aren't going to like you for it. In fact, they're actually going to hate you, some of them.

00:23:38.075 --> 00:23:53.169
And the more you get popular in this world,"He said, "Brandon, you'll have millions of people come and there's going to be people who actually despise you, but you're supposed to say—you'll say what I say.

00:23:53.170 --> 00:24:00.759
And don't be moved by what they think about you. Fear Me, not them."And I'll do it.

00:24:00.760 --> 00:24:07.599
I'll do it. Just as country as I can be. Just sit back and say, "God, I will follow You.

00:24:07.600 --> 00:24:13.391
I will follow You even if it's not popular."But we pray for our government.

00:24:13.392 --> 00:24:20.652
We pray for things because I know a storm's coming. I know a storm's coming.

00:24:20.653 --> 00:24:27.439
And if you don't have the word down in your heart, I tell you again, ladies and gentlemen, we will be here for some of this stuff.

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:36.239
And you have no idea. I've seen into the next four years. I've seen the things that are coming.

